<h1>Editing Article</h1>
<p>If the eddited article were already tweeted, the tweet will be destroyed.</p><br>
<p>Moshi henshu sita kiji ga sude ni tweet sareteita baai, tweet wa sakujo saremasu.</p>

<%= form_for @article do |f| %>
  <%= f.text_area :content, cols: 40, rows: 5 ,maxlength: 140 %><br>
  <%= f.submit 'edit' %>
<% end %>

<%= link_to 'Show', @article %> |
<%= link_to 'Back', articles_path %>
